arts.sum: Dango Ouattara scored an 89th-minute equaliser as Bournemouth snatched a point in a 2-2 draw with Fulham at Craven Cottage. Raúl Jiménez scored his sixth Premier League goal of the season before Evanilson struck early in the second half to level.
